In your verse:

Vaporeon = female (normally)

Flareon = male (normally)

If they appear swapped (male Vaporeon, female Flareon), it’s explicitly due to VBend’s genderbending system, not actual identity change.

I’ll treat those VR transformations as in-universe temporary gender presentation flips, not actual pronoun/gender shifts.

So next time, no mix-ups. No excuses. No second miracles.

